data.description: ***PRICE DROP!!!***Seller is willing to pay for 2% buy down on your  interest rate to make this the best house payment out there.   In the coveted neighborhood of Gardendale Park, sitting on a level lot with a circular drive, sits a full brick beauty that has been updated with an open floor plan and brand new kitchen with a super sized island with granite countertops, new cabinetry with soft close drawers/doors, and new appliances.  Along with the large open great room and kitchen, there is also a lovely sunroom and large covered deck.  There is a massive laundry room with plenty of room to do crafts or have full sized freezers or a sewing room.  There are 3 generous bedrooms and 2 baths plus a full unfinished basement allowing you the opportunity to have more space designed just for you.   All of this with a beautifully manicured lawn and private back yard.   Come see and make this your next forever home!
